This program deletes files older than one week in specified folder.

Call with:
ruby delete-outbox.rb /home/user/Downloads/Outbox

Crontab example:
59 * * * * ruby /home/user/bin/delete-outbox/delete-outbox.rb /home/user/Downloads/Outbox
This will check for files to delete every 59th minute in every hour, every day, all year.
